p is a big fan of talismans, human baubles he keeps close and effectively r=
ubs for good luck. Tulsi seems to have become his latest rabbit=E2=80=99s f=
oot.<br/><br/>Harris is doing debate prep in the more traditional way, hunk=
ered down in Pittsburgh with a team led by D.C. power lawyer <b>Karen Dunn<=
/b>. Some political observers were surprised that Harris didn=E2=80=99t go =
with <b>Ron Klain</b>, the most widely revered debate prep impresario in th=
