hilippe is fantastically good at mimicking Trump=E2=80=99s chaotic onstage =
presence.<br/><br/>Last week, Trump told <b>Sean Hannity</b> that his debat=
e strategy is to let Kamala talk, believing that letting her prattle on wil=
